---
description: Billing and payment rules for Robokassa work.
globs:
  - src/modules/billing/**/*
  - src/app/api/robokassa/**/*
  - src/lib/security.ts
---

Billing must stay isolated:
- Keep payment logic inside the billing module.
- Treat `ResultURL` as the source of truth.
- Validate the signature before any state change.
- Make webhook handlers idempotent.
- Persist order, payment event, and enrollment updates transactionally.

